These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
House: art-deco, cottage, tower, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, russian, spanish, turkish
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, apricot, tomato, pear
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, april, september
 1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
 2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 3. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person eating pear is the russian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 7. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 9. the tower house is on the left or right of the spanish##3
10. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the art-deco house##7
11. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
12. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
13. the person who's birthday is in september is the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House   | futuristic    | cottage | tower    | art-deco   |
| Nationality   | colombian | spanish | russian | turkish |
| Food           | apricot       | tomato   | pear  | kiwi     |
| Birthday     | march      | april   | september    | june    |

