.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, taxi, ship, tram
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, chaman, blend, ritmeester
City: hamburg, san-francisco, london, berlin
 1. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 2. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
 4. the person traveling to london is the siglo-smoker##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 6. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 7. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the siglo-smoker##7
 8. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
11. the chaman-smoker is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | roller   | ship       | tram    | taxi      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Cigar   | ritmeester   | siglo  | chaman       | blend |
| City         | hamburg      | london  | berlin | san-francisco |

