10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage         | 7up      | hot-chocolate   | juice   | iced-tea       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| Flower   | sunflower  | daffodil | tulip   | begonia     |
| Transport         | helicopter   | quad-bike    | train   | snowmobile |

