 6. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the paramedic##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5
 9. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
