.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, hiking, singing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, davidoff, fonseca, bongani
City: liverpool, paris, prague, miami
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, 7up, cola
 1. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 2. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 5. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is the person drinking milk##1
 9. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
10. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
12. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | singing      | hiking     | cooking   | baking    |
| Cigar     | bongani | fonseca   | davidoff | siglo |
| City     | miami        | prague     | liverpool  | paris      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea       | cola | milk   | 7up    |

 